snippet.title: Sleepi Boi Can't Sleep - 3D Bitsy Game
snippet.description:
Play it here: https://thatsmaik.itch.io/sleepi-boi-cant-sleep

I made a Bitsy 3D game for the november Bitsy game jam. The theme was "SLEEPY". It's my first ever Bitsy game, let me know what you think.
